<h1>Dido (2021)</h1>

<p>
High-order ambisonic stage work.  
Commissioned by 212 Festival (Istanbul).  
Premiered at Bilkent International Laboratory Theatre, Ankara.
</p>

<p>
Dido explores spatialized sound, immersive listening environments,
and the relationship between voice, memory, and political resonance.
</p>

